      "groupIds": [
        "f1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A=26  B=25  C=24  D=23  E=22  F=21  G=20  H=19  I=18\nJ=17  K=16  L=15  M=14  N=13  O=12  P=11  Q=10  R=9\nS=8   T=7   U=6   V=5   W=4   X=3   Y=2   Z=1\n\nWHY: 26 letters total. Reverse pos = 27-Fwd.\n  A is 1st from front = 26th from back.\n\nEx: G = 7 forward → 27-7 = 20 reverse",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
