    {
      "id": "el_23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 673,
      "width": 404,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Find shift: C(3)->D(4), A(1)->B(2), T(20)->U(21)\nStep 2: Each letter shifted by +1\nStep 3: Apply to DOG: D->E, O->P, G->H\n\n  C ─+1─> D , A ─+1─> B , T ─+1─> U  (all +1)\n  D ─+1─> E , O ─+1─> P , G ─+1─> H\n\nTRICK:\nAll diffs same? Uniform shift!\nJust add +1 to each letter of DOG.\nWrap-around: Z+1=A\n\nAnswer: EPH ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
