      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Find shift: C(3)->D(4), A(1)->B(2), T(20)->U(21)\nStep 2: Each letter shifted by +1\nStep 3: Apply to DOG: D->E, O->P, G->H\n\n  C ─+1─> D , A ─+1─> B , T ─+1─> U  (all +1)\n  D ─+1─> E , O ─+1─> P , G ─+1─> H\n\nTRICK:\nAll diffs same? Uniform shift!\nJust add +1 to each letter of DOG.\nWrap-around: Z+1=A\n\nAnswer: EPH ✓",
