    {
      "id": "el_28",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 673,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: C(3)+X(24)=27, O(15)+L(12)=27\nStep 2: M(13)+N(14)=27, E(5)+V(22)=27\nStep 3: Rule: each pair sums to 27\n\n  A B C D ... M N ... W X Y Z\n  Z Y X W ... N M ...  D C B A\n  (mirror: each pair sums to 27)\n  B->Y  O->L  N->M  D->W\n\nTRICK:\nAll sums = 27? Mirror coding!\nFormula: New = 27 - Old position\n\nAnswer: YLMW ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 28,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: C(3)+X(24)=27, O(15)+L(12)=27\nStep 2: M(13)+N(14)=27, E(5)+V(22)=27\nStep 3: Rule: each pair sums to 27\n\n  A B C D ... M N ... W X Y Z\n  Z Y X W ... N M ...  D C B A\n  (mirror: each pair sums to 27)\n  B->Y  O->L  N->M  D->W\n\nTRICK:\nAll sums = 27? Mirror coding!\nFormula: New = 27 - Old position\n\nAnswer: YLMW ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
