    {
      "id": "el_43",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1071,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B(cons)->prev->A, O(vow)->next->P\nStep 2: A(vow)->next->B, R(cons)->prev->Q\nStep 3: D(cons)->prev->C\n\n  B    O    A    R    D\n  C    V    V    C    C    <- type\n  -1   +1   +1   -1   -1  <- shift\n  A    P    B    Q    C   = APBQC\n\nTRICK:\nSplit word: mark V/C above each letter.\nV: shift +1, C: shift -1.\n\nAnswer: APBQC ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
