      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B(cons)->prev->A, O(vow)->next->P\nStep 2: A(vow)->next->B, R(cons)->prev->Q\nStep 3: D(cons)->prev->C\n\n  B    O    A    R    D\n  C    V    V    C    C    <- type\n  -1   +1   +1   -1   -1  <- shift\n  A    P    B    Q    C   = APBQC\n\nTRICK:\nSplit word: mark V/C above each letter.\nV: shift +1, C: shift -1.\n\nAnswer: APBQC ✓",
