    {
      "id": "el_53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1453,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: ROAD=5312: R=5,O=3,A=1,D=2\nStep 2: SHIRT=64850: S=6,H=4,I=8,R=5,T=0\nStep 3: R=5 in both -> consistent ✓\n\n  Map: R->5  O->3  A->1  D->2\n       S->6  H->4  I->8  T->0\n  THIS: T=0  H=4  I=8  S=6 -> 0486\n\nTRICK:\nBuild letter->number map from given pairs.\nSame letter MUST map to same number!\n\nAnswer: 0486 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
