        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: ROAD=5312: R=5,O=3,A=1,D=2\nStep 2: SHIRT=64850: S=6,H=4,I=8,R=5,T=0\nStep 3: R=5 in both -> consistent ✓\n\n  Map: R->5  O->3  A->1  D->2\n       S->6  H->4  I->8  T->0\n  THIS: T=0  H=4  I=8  S=6 -> 0486\n\nTRICK:\nBuild letter->number map from given pairs.\nSame letter MUST map to same number!\n\nAnswer: 0486 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
