    {
      "id": "el_58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1469,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Replace ALL symbols first\n  8 + 6 - 3 x 2 / 1\n  8 x 6 / 3 - 2 + 1\nStep 2: BODMAS: 48/3 - 2 + 1 = 15\n\n  Code:  + means x  ,  - means /\n         x means -  ,  / means +\n  8 + 6 - 3 x 2 / 1\n  8 x 6 / 3 - 2 + 1 = 48/3 - 2 + 1 = 15\n\nTRICK:\nWrite substitution table on side.\nReplace ALL at once, THEN solve.\nTRAP: Don't solve while replacing!\n\nAnswer: 15 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
