      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Replace ALL symbols first\n  8 + 6 - 3 x 2 / 1\n  8 x 6 / 3 - 2 + 1\nStep 2: BODMAS: 48/3 - 2 + 1 = 15\n\n  Code:  + means x  ,  - means /\n         x means -  ,  / means +\n  8 + 6 - 3 x 2 / 1\n  8 x 6 / 3 - 2 + 1 = 48/3 - 2 + 1 = 15\n\nTRICK:\nWrite substitution table on side.\nReplace ALL at once, THEN solve.\nTRAP: Don't solve while replacing!\n\nAnswer: 15 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
