    {
      "id": "el_63",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1469,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Common word \"home\" in both\nStep 2: Common code \"pa\" in both\nStep 3: home = pa. From \"go home\"=\"la pa\"\n  -> go = la\n\n  \"go   home\"      = \"la  pa\"\n  \"come home fast\" = \"na  pa  ta\"\n         ^^^^           ^^^\n   Common: home = pa\n   Remaining: go = la\n\nTRICK:\nFind COMMON words -> COMMON codes\nEliminate known -> find unknown\n\nAnswer: go = la ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
