      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Common word \"home\" in both\nStep 2: Common code \"pa\" in both\nStep 3: home = pa. From \"go home\"=\"la pa\"\n  -> go = la\n\n  \"go   home\"      = \"la  pa\"\n  \"come home fast\" = \"na  pa  ta\"\n         ^^^^           ^^^\n   Common: home = pa\n   Remaining: go = la\n\nTRICK:\nFind COMMON words -> COMMON codes\nEliminate known -> find unknown\n\nAnswer: go = la ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
